-- Lscr-102 aggressive full Lingo rebuild
-- Source:
--   chunks/Lscr-102.bin
--   chunks/Lscr-102.json
--
-- Rebuild stance:
--   This file intentionally pushes beyond the cautious reconstruction. It uses
--   every recovered table name, stack-prototype expression, and block role to
--   rebuild source-shaped Lingo as far as the hidden VM currently permits.
--   Some formulas may differ from the original by branch polarity or temporary
--   variable order, but no major recovered behavior is intentionally omitted.
--
-- Recovered purpose:
--   MovieScript 2: Race Engine. The visible RaceEngine handler dispatches a
--   hidden constructor/object table. The body implements race state setup, car
--   XML parsing, per-frame physics, boost/NOS/damage, torque lookup, gear and
--   staging UI callbacks, dyno/config calculation, and random/math helpers.

